> [!CAUTION]
> In active development! Cannot be used in real projects!
> 

## Install
```bash
pip install jamlib
```

## Getting start
```python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-

from typing import Any

from jam import Jam

config: dict[str, Any] = {
        "jwt_secret_key": "some-secret",
        "expire": 3600
    }

data = {
    "user_id": 1,
    "role": "admin"
}

jam = Jam(auth_type="jwt", config=config)

payload = jam.make_payload(**data)
token = jam.gen_jwt_token(**payload)
```

